{"tid":1930854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國有一婦人留假姓名檢測，呈陽性後遁逃消失","createTime":"2020-03-18T00:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T01:18:22.000Z","uid":64191,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"56e95f05a354128cb46da0f3f59032f3200ead26","tid":1930854,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T00:15:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/X6kdK7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2FX6kdK7&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=66c77f68\" target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/X6kdK7</a><br />\n<br />\n美國新澤西州 Newark (紐華克)，有一名婦女在 3月14日的時候到當地一家醫院（East Orange General Hospital)檢測武漢肺炎，結果呈現陽性。<br />\n<br />\n當地衛生部門到其於醫院登錄的住址拜訪，卻發現她留下的是假姓名、假地址，那個地址查無此人。<br />\n<br />\n她檢測呈陽性，然後消失在茫茫人海中。於是地方政府(警方)，向法院申請了搜查命令，翻閱醫院有關該名婦人的影像畫面，又呼籲該婦人盡快現身<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩，移動生化武器，美國人既日常事件出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e78bfb38b0696491a742ae5af44533f0c61e7e","tid":1930854,"uid":260657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T00:20:52.000Z","msg":"生化武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6b62ab7de1a3dde9ea68aea8754b0f9701feeb","tid":1930854,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T00:52:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a2c2b8f0e4cb4fc2e1c8678f495f7c1642f0abd","tid":1930854,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a6b62ab7de1a3dde9ea68aea8754b0f9701feeb","tid":1930854,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T00:52:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:14:50.000Z","msg":"美國冇身分證，佢哋用駕駛執照核實身份"},{"pid"